subject: QS doesn't stay on line

messageBody:
Truely, I love Quikscript along with shorthand (especially Gregg and
Groote). I encountered the following problem when using Quikscript Senior;

it just doesn't stay on the line. When I write a particular word I
often need to interrupt the stroke in order to keep on the line. To me
that's very annoying as it gets the speed out of my writing.

Is interrupting the only way to stay on the line?

Ramses
